videos.headline: Hall drops in 28-yard dime to Nacua for a BYU TD
videos.description: Caleb Lohner grabs the steal and tosses ahead to Gavin Baxter for the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hall drops in 28-yard dime to Nacua for a BYU TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU's Nacua leaves the field after helmet flies off on hit
videos.description: Puka Nacua is slow to get up after he loses his helmet on a hard hit.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU's Nacua leaves the field after helmet flies off on hit) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU scores TD after USC's FG penalty
videos.description: USC commits an offside penalty on BYU's field goal, the Cougars accept the penalty and get a 9-yard touchdown from Tyler Allgeier.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU scores TD after USC's FG penalty) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: USC's Jaxson Dart takes the fumbled snap into the end zone
videos.description: Jaxson Dart corrals the fumble and takes it in for the 6-yard USC touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (USC's Jaxson Dart takes the fumbled snap into the end zone) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU TE gets carted off after suffering injury
videos.description: Isaac Rex has to be carted off the field after he lands awkwardly on an incomplete catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU TE gets carted off after suffering injury) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyler Allgeier breaks tackles for his second BYU TD
videos.description: Tyler Allgeier refuses to be denied the end zone for his second touchdown of the night.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tyler Allgeier breaks tackles for his second BYU TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaren Hall drops in 41-yard TD dime right over USC DB
videos.description: Jaren Hall throws a stellar 41-yard pass to Keanu Hill for the BYU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jaren Hall drops in 41-yard TD dime right over USC DB) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vavae Malepeai bounces off a tackle for the USC TD
videos.description: Vavae Malepeai bulldozes into the end zone for the 2-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Vavae Malepeai bounces off a tackle for the USC TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaxson Dart tosses TD, 2-pt conversion to put USC ahead
videos.description: Jaxson Dart finds Gary Bryant Jr. for the touchdown and follows up with a pass to Lake McRee for the 2-point conversion to give USC the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jaxson Dart tosses TD, 2-pt conversion to put USC ahead) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Calen Bullock makes clutch end zone INT for USC
videos.description: Jaren Hall's long shot into the end zone gets picked off by Calen Bullock for a touchback.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Calen Bullock makes clutch end zone INT for USC) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU converts recovered fumble into TD
videos.description: USC forces Tyler Allgeier to fumble but teammate Dallin Holker recovers and runs it 22 yards to set up the touchdown from Jackson McChesney.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU converts recovered fumble into TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU's Kaleb Hayes takes a bow after game-saving stop
videos.description: Kaleb Hayes comes up clutch for BYU with a big stop on USC's fourth down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU's Kaleb Hayes takes a bow after game-saving stop) 2021/11/28 ESHEET
